4. EDUCATION MODULES (FULL SCRIPTS)
MODULE 1 â€“ Understanding the Addiction
Lesson 1: This Is Not a Habit â€” Itâ€™s an Addiction
Most people call smoking or vaping a â€œhabit.â€
Itâ€™s not a habit. Itâ€™s an addiction.

A habit is something you consciously choose.
Addiction is something that controls you.

If it was a habit, you could simply stop.
If it was a habit, you wouldnâ€™t think about it every hour.
If it was a habit, you wouldnâ€™t panic without nicotine.

Nicotine rewires your brain to crave the next dose.

Youâ€™re not weak.
The nicotine is powerful.
