Lesson 2: Why You Light Up Without Thinking
Every smoker knows this moment:
You look down and realize you lit a cigarette or grabbed your vape without even realizing it.

Nicotine builds automatic behaviors.

You donâ€™t think.
You donâ€™t choose.
You react.

Your brain has learned:
