10. CALCULATOR LOGIC
Inputs per user (examples):

cigarettes_per_day

cigarettes_per_pack (default 20)

pack_price

avg_minutes_per_cigarette (default 5)

vape_daily_spend

vape_sessions_per_day (optional)

avg_minutes_per_vape_session

pouches_per_day

pouches_per_can (default 20)

pouch_can_price

avg_minutes_per_pouch

cans_per_week (dip)

dip_can_price

dip_sessions_per_day

avg_minutes_per_dip_session

Cost Calculations
Cigarettes:

packs_per_day = cigarettes_per_day / cigarettes_per_pack

cig_daily_cost = packs_per_day * pack_price

cig_monthly_cost = cig_daily_cost * 30

cig_yearly_cost = cig_daily_cost * 365

cig_5yr_cost = cig_yearly_cost * 5

Similar for vape, pouches, dip using daily or weekly spend.

Time Spent
Cigarettes:

cig_minutes_per_day = cigarettes_per_day * avg_minutes_per_cigarette

cig_hours_per_day = cig_minutes_per_day / 60

cig_hours_per_year = cig_hours_per_day * 365

cig_days_per_year = cig_hours_per_year / 24

Apply same pattern to vape, pouches, dip.

Mixed Use
Sum costs and time across product types:

total_daily_cost

total_monthly_cost

total_yearly_cost

total_5yr_cost

total_minutes_per_day â†’ hours â†’ days per year

Since Quit
days_since_quit = (now - quit_datetime) in days

money_saved = total_daily_cost * days_since_quit

units_avoided per product: usage_per_day * days_since_quit

minutes_freed = total_minutes_per_day * days_since_quit

Optional life-days regained estimate based on a simple constant.

